---
title: Double Plant-Based Chick'n & Soy Slaw Tacos with Sriracha Mayo & Spring Onion
description: May we introduce your new vegetarian friendly favourite, the plant-based chick'n taco. Golden and glowing, the sriracha mayo combo really brings out the best in this dish and goes nicely with slaw, all put together in a warm taco. Delish!
